1
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:41,039
[The Epoch of Miyu]

2
00:01:41,050 --> 00:01:43,979
[Episode 27]

3
00:02:03,250 --> 00:02:05,430
[Shanghai Hongkou District
Central Hospital]

4
00:02:05,450 --> 00:02:08,259
[Gastroscopy Diagnosis Report]

5
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:10,759
[Diagnosis: Massive protruding lesion
at the cardia]

6
00:02:10,789 --> 00:02:13,720
[[Highly suspected malignant
characteristics]]

7
00:02:16,500 --> 00:02:20,079
[Ke Wenxue]

8
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:17,640
Hey everyone,

9
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:19,800
I heard Purong is about to enter
a close collaboration

10
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:20,930
with Jiang Zhichun.

11
00:02:20,460 --> 00:02:21,400
[Luo Qingping]

12
00:02:21,470 --> 00:02:22,430
What's going on?

13
00:02:22,010 --> 00:02:22,829
[Yin Xiang]

14
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,430
You guys didn't know?

15
00:02:24,430 --> 00:02:26,490
Mr. Ji and Jiang Zhichun are a couple.

16
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:27,520
Wow,

17
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:28,840
a power couple team-up,

18
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:29,960
total double A energy.

19
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:30,870
It's raining.

20
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:32,850
Hurry and bring the laundry in.

21
00:02:36,079 --> 00:02:37,280
Focus on your work,

22
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:38,450
Xu Miyu.

23
00:02:43,730 --> 00:02:45,460
Quick, get the clothes inside.

24
00:02:48,340 --> 00:02:50,190
Why is it raining again?

25
00:03:10,420 --> 00:03:11,290
Coming.

26
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:17,750
Lu Xiaoyan?

27
00:03:18,030 --> 00:03:18,820
What's the matter?

28
00:03:18,820 --> 00:03:19,660
Ms. Xu,

29
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:21,079
does our hotel have any discount policies

30
00:03:21,079 --> 00:03:22,630
during the college entrance exam period?

31
00:03:22,630 --> 00:03:23,310
Come in and talk first.

32
00:03:23,310 --> 00:03:23,930
Sure.

33
00:03:25,470 --> 00:03:27,710
My cousin is taking the college
entrance exam this year,

34
00:03:27,710 --> 00:03:29,630
and his test center is right
near our Purong Hotel.

35
00:03:29,630 --> 00:03:32,110
It's a newly added exam site, I heard.

36
00:03:32,150 --> 00:03:32,910
My aunt was thinking

37
00:03:32,910 --> 00:03:34,840
of booking a room here

38
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:36,910
for him during the exams,

39
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:39,400
but she's worried it'll be too expensive.

40
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:41,240
So she asked me to check

41
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:43,030
if there are any special offers.

42
00:03:43,030 --> 00:03:45,910
They're just regular working-class folks,

43
00:03:46,190 --> 00:03:47,310
you know how it is, Ms. Xu.

44
00:03:47,310 --> 00:03:48,280
I understand.

45
00:03:48,750 --> 00:03:50,470
Is that new exam site

46
00:03:50,470 --> 00:03:52,240
the Xinhua Finance and Economics School

47
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:53,500
over on Yanghuai Road?

48
00:03:54,030 --> 00:03:55,280
You already knew.

49
00:03:58,750 --> 00:03:59,870
I was actually planning

50
00:03:59,870 --> 00:04:01,470
to head over there tomorrow
to check it out.

51
00:04:01,470 --> 00:04:02,840
Look, it's right here.

52
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:04,240
If

53
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:06,120
the scale and location work out well,

54
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,400
I want to submit an application
to the hotel

55
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:09,190
for a special discount for exam-takers.

56
00:04:09,190 --> 00:04:10,400
That'd be amazing!

57
00:04:10,630 --> 00:04:11,960
Take me with you then.

58
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:14,030
I wanna scope out the exam site
for my cousin too.

59
00:04:14,030 --> 00:04:14,680
Deal.

60
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:23,630
Here we are.

61
00:04:23,700 --> 00:04:28,310
[Xinhua Finance and Economics School
Police Service Office]

62
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:28,510
It only took us

63
00:04:28,370 --> 00:04:30,990
[Timer]

64
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,000
eleven minutes on foot
from the hotel lobby

65
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:31,190
to get here.

66
00:04:31,190 --> 00:04:31,950
That walking distance

67
00:04:31,950 --> 00:04:33,240
is pretty ideal.

68
00:04:33,690 --> 00:04:36,420
But what if the guest room elevators
get crowded?

69
00:04:36,630 --> 00:04:37,750
If that happens,

70
00:04:37,750 --> 00:04:38,800
we'll make

71
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:40,330
a staggered schedule plan,

72
00:04:41,030 --> 00:04:42,430
assign specific

73
00:04:42,430 --> 00:04:43,770
elevator time slots by floor.

74
00:04:43,770 --> 00:04:46,090
We'll need the Housekeeping team
to cooperate,

75
00:04:46,090 --> 00:04:47,750
have attendants on each floor help
keep order during that time.

76
00:04:47,750 --> 00:04:50,010
help maintain order when the time comes.

77
00:04:50,110 --> 00:04:51,159
Ms. Xu,

78
00:04:51,190 --> 00:04:52,460
you're so thoughtful.

79
00:04:52,510 --> 00:04:54,040
The college entrance exam only comes
once in a lifetime,

80
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:56,000
it's every family's top priority.

81
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:59,210
We should always go the extra mile
for our guests.

82
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:00,310
Let's go.

83
00:05:02,460 --> 00:05:03,790
Who are you looking for?

84
00:05:04,590 --> 00:05:06,990
Sir, please let us take
a quick look inside.

85
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:08,430
We just wanna walk around for a minute.

86
00:05:08,430 --> 00:05:09,240
Walk around?

87
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:10,820
If anything goes missing in here,
I'll get blamed for it.

88
00:05:10,820 --> 00:05:11,680
This is my sister.

89
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:12,750
She's taking the college
entrance exam soon.

90
00:05:12,750 --> 00:05:14,510
I wanted to bring her to get
familiar with the area,

91
00:05:14,510 --> 00:05:15,680
so she won't get

92
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:16,870
too nervous on exam day

93
00:05:16,870 --> 00:05:18,160
and mess up her mood.

94
00:05:18,510 --> 00:05:19,160
Exactly.

95
00:05:19,180 --> 00:05:20,800
We just wanna see the classrooms

96
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:22,360
and get familiar with the route.

97
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:23,300
Exam-takers, huh?

98
00:05:23,300 --> 00:05:24,460
Can't be too careful with that.

99
00:05:24,460 --> 00:05:25,920
Wait a second, I'll unlock the door.

100
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:26,920
Thank you so much.

101
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:32,610
[Reminder: No unauthorized entry
for outsiders]

102
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:32,510
Come on, this way.

103
00:05:32,510 --> 00:05:33,159
Let's go.

104
00:05:40,630 --> 00:05:41,430
Director Bai.

105
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:42,040
Save whatever

106
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:43,190
you need to say for after my meeting.

107
00:05:43,190 --> 00:05:43,990
I'm gonna be late.

108
00:05:43,990 --> 00:05:46,320
This might come in handy for your meeting.

109
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:49,430
I put this together over
the past few days,

110
00:05:49,430 --> 00:05:51,090
a full research report on this year's
college entrance exam sites.

111
00:05:51,090 --> 00:05:52,150
Please take a look.

112
00:05:52,820 --> 00:05:53,750
[Shanghai College Entrance Exam Site
Research Report]

113
00:05:53,750 --> 00:05:54,670
[Table of Contents]

114
00:05:53,830 --> 00:05:54,750
Five new exam sites

115
00:05:54,750 --> 00:05:56,280
have been added across the city this year,

116
00:05:56,280 --> 00:05:58,190
and one's located right next
to our hotel —

117
00:05:58,190 --> 00:05:59,620
Xinhua Finance and Economics School.

118
00:05:59,620 --> 00:06:00,800
I've already checked the location
in person,

119
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:01,720
the information is confirmed,

120
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:03,300
and they're already setting up
the exam classrooms.

121
00:06:03,300 --> 00:06:04,860
What does any of this

122
00:06:04,880 --> 00:06:06,340
have to do with my meeting?

123
00:06:07,110 --> 00:06:09,260
These people are all potential customers.

124
00:06:09,260 --> 00:06:10,840
Exam students, their parents,

125
00:06:10,840 --> 00:06:12,680
even the exam supervisors.

126
00:06:13,230 --> 00:06:14,310
Didn't Mr. Ji urge

127
00:06:14,310 --> 00:06:15,720
all management staff
to brainstorm new business ideas?

128
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:17,920
This is ridiculous for
potential customers.

129
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:18,870
Let me tell you,

130
00:06:18,890 --> 00:06:21,560
people buried in exam stress
have nothing on their minds but the test.

131
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:23,510
Even if you offered them a luxury
five-star hotel stay,

132
00:06:23,510 --> 00:06:24,750
they wouldn't be in the mood for it.

133
00:06:24,750 --> 00:06:27,430
Plus, there are tons of
budget hotels nearby.

134
00:06:27,430 --> 00:06:28,830
We can't compete with them

135
00:06:28,830 --> 00:06:30,310
for exam-taker business.

136
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:32,390
Regular families on a budget

137
00:06:32,390 --> 00:06:35,250
aren't gonna splurge on a fancy hotel
for the exams.

138
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:36,500
Director Bai,

139
00:06:36,500 --> 00:06:38,500
this isn't just wishful thinking.

140
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:38,950
Recently,

141
00:06:38,950 --> 00:06:39,920
we've been getting booking inquiries

142
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:41,000
one after another

143
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:42,810
for stays during the exam period.

144
00:06:42,810 --> 00:06:43,430
And this is all

145
00:06:43,430 --> 00:06:45,480
without any official discounts

146
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:47,500
or promotional ads launched yet.

147
00:06:47,530 --> 00:06:50,340
I believe there's huge untapped
business potential here.

148
00:06:50,340 --> 00:06:51,630
Shi Huanhuan compiled all

149
00:06:51,630 --> 00:06:53,040
the reservation data,

150
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:54,100
please take a look.

151
00:06:54,210 --> 00:06:56,890
[Purong Hotel Walk-In Reservation Summary]

152
00:06:56,270 --> 00:06:59,000
That's only a dozen bookings total.

153
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,810
Not even enough to fill one floor.

154
00:07:00,810 --> 00:07:02,070
And we can't even confirm

155
00:07:02,070 --> 00:07:04,220
they're all exam families.

156
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:07,360
This idea's not half as good as Mr. Ji's
rain-viewing group.

157
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:08,000
Ms. Xu,

158
00:07:08,510 --> 00:07:09,580
it's not worth the effort.

159
00:07:09,580 --> 00:07:11,040
I appreciate the initiative though.

160
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:13,440
Come find me later if you
have better ideas.

161
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:14,480
I'm seriously running late

162
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:15,340
for my meeting.

163
00:07:19,770 --> 00:07:20,990
We'll talk later.

164
00:07:21,150 --> 00:07:22,550
Take care, Director Bai.

165
00:07:28,320 --> 00:07:30,720
[Purong Hotel, Enduring
Rivers, Lasting Glory]

166
00:07:30,740 --> 00:07:34,340
[Purong Hotel, Always By Your Side]

167
00:07:33,070 --> 00:07:34,120
In my opinion,

168
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:38,190
Mr. Ji, there’s no need for you
to worry too much.

169
00:07:39,310 --> 00:07:41,750
Hasn't the rain-viewing group checked in
these past two days?

170
00:07:41,750 --> 00:07:43,870
You're right, occupancy is way better

171
00:07:43,870 --> 00:07:44,870
than it was

172
00:07:44,870 --> 00:07:47,120
this same time last year.

173
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:48,090
Besides,

174
00:07:48,870 --> 00:07:49,950
even the best scenic spots

175
00:07:49,950 --> 00:07:51,190
have off and peak seasons.

176
00:07:51,190 --> 00:07:51,870
Right?

177
00:07:52,520 --> 00:07:53,310
Our hotel

178
00:07:53,310 --> 00:07:55,120
operates in the same cycle.

179
00:07:55,140 --> 00:07:55,830
And,

180
00:07:55,980 --> 00:07:56,659
it's also

181
00:07:57,400 --> 00:07:58,760
rainy season right now,

182
00:07:59,500 --> 00:08:00,850
slower business is totally normal.

183
00:08:00,850 --> 00:08:02,580
Director Huang's right.

184
00:08:02,750 --> 00:08:05,120
Our hotel's current operating state

185
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:06,580
isn't so much a bottleneck

186
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,120
as it's just

187
00:08:08,310 --> 00:08:11,000
hitting a regular seasonal low point.

188
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:13,750
Other hotels are also...

189
00:08:13,750 --> 00:08:16,660
Off-season management doesn't
mean we just let things slide.

190
00:08:16,660 --> 00:08:18,790
Tourism fluctuates with the weather,

191
00:08:18,800 --> 00:08:20,460
but business doesn't have to.

192
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:21,680
Beyond tourist stays,

193
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:22,900
our hotel can host

194
00:08:23,390 --> 00:08:25,710
corporate events,

195
00:08:26,510 --> 00:08:28,240
and offer premium fine dining.

196
00:08:29,820 --> 00:08:32,490
I want everyone to think outside the box

197
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:35,039
and actively explore new
business opportunities.

198
00:08:35,039 --> 00:08:36,150
[Dad, I miss you.]

199
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:37,970
Alright then, since Mr. Ji
put it that way…

200
00:08:37,940 --> 00:08:39,700
[Daughter]

201
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:40,120
We need to chase new
business opportunities.

202
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:41,000
Director Qian,

203
00:08:41,510 --> 00:08:42,909
do you have any insights?

204
00:08:48,410 --> 00:08:49,210
Director Bai.

205
00:08:49,810 --> 00:08:50,690
Director Bai!

206
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:55,000
Here.

207
00:08:55,550 --> 00:08:56,350
What's wrong?

208
00:08:57,020 --> 00:08:58,020
Director Bai.

209
00:08:58,930 --> 00:09:01,710
Everyone's waiting for your input.

210
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:02,630
Me?

211
00:09:04,640 --> 00:09:05,700
Alright.

212
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:06,840
Let's not

213
00:09:07,030 --> 00:09:08,820
pressure Director Bai.

214
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:09,750
After all,

215
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:13,500
it's not the Front Office's
place to worry about this.

216
00:09:16,750 --> 00:09:17,750
To be honest,

217
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:19,940
I've been thinking about something lately.

218
00:09:19,940 --> 00:09:20,570
Go ahead.

219
00:09:21,540 --> 00:09:23,030
What if we tapped into

220
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:26,360
the college entrance exam crowd
for new business?

221
00:09:28,580 --> 00:09:29,120
Look how

222
00:09:29,120 --> 00:09:30,990
desperate we've gotten.

223
00:09:32,110 --> 00:09:32,960
Director Bai,

224
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:34,000
the college entrance exam,

225
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:36,630
high school students aren't tour groups.

226
00:09:37,500 --> 00:09:38,390
They're not

227
00:09:38,410 --> 00:09:41,070
here for a vacation right before
their big exam.

228
00:09:42,110 --> 00:09:43,200
Though you never know,

229
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:45,080
maybe this year's exam essay prompt

230
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:46,780
will be all about Purong Hotel.

231
00:09:46,780 --> 00:09:48,000
After all, our hotel boasts

232
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:50,240
nearly half a century of
remarkable history.

233
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:51,000
Right?

234
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:53,260
Mr. Huang, I've done thorough research.

235
00:09:53,670 --> 00:09:54,360
Mr. Ji,

236
00:09:54,420 --> 00:09:55,260
look at

237
00:09:55,280 --> 00:09:58,400
what you've driven us to.

238
00:09:58,680 --> 00:10:01,390
Even Front Office Director Bai Yongjun

239
00:10:01,410 --> 00:10:02,970
is doing market research now.

240
00:10:02,970 --> 00:10:04,170
That's a great thing.

241
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:06,660
It just shows everyone's full
of potential.

242
00:10:07,660 --> 00:10:08,400
Go on,

243
00:10:09,040 --> 00:10:09,900
Director Bai.

244
00:10:09,980 --> 00:10:10,840
I...

245
00:10:12,400 --> 00:10:13,000
Well…

246
00:10:13,670 --> 00:10:15,180
I found out a new exam site

247
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:17,000
was added this year,

248
00:10:17,020 --> 00:10:18,690
right next to our hotel.

249
00:10:19,090 --> 00:10:20,150
How close exactly?

250
00:10:20,290 --> 00:10:21,090
Pretty close,

251
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:23,680
not far at all.

252
00:10:24,490 --> 00:10:26,560
What's the name of the new site?

253
00:10:27,040 --> 00:10:27,870
It's…

254
00:10:30,480 --> 00:10:32,480
Where did you get this information?

255
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:34,290
Municipal Education Commission website?

256
00:10:34,290 --> 00:10:36,520
Exam Authority official site?

257
00:10:37,750 --> 00:10:39,550
How many exam seats does it have?

258
00:10:39,670 --> 00:10:41,870
What's the background of the students?

259
00:10:47,470 --> 00:10:48,730
It's fine, Director Bai,

260
00:10:48,730 --> 00:10:49,850
don't be nervous.

261
00:10:49,880 --> 00:10:50,750
Did you do this research alone,

262
00:10:50,750 --> 00:10:51,840
or with help?

263
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:53,840
We collaborated on it.

264
00:10:53,870 --> 00:10:55,000
There's another team member

265
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:56,460
who knows all the details.

266
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:57,960
I can go get her.

267
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:00,030
Please do.

268
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:09,320
Send Ms. Xu to

269
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:10,150
the conference room immediately.

270
00:11:10,150 --> 00:11:10,810
Chop, chop!

271
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:12,060
We're all waiting.

272
00:11:24,210 --> 00:11:24,970
Ms. Xu,

273
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:26,500
this might actually work out!

274
00:11:26,500 --> 00:11:27,960
Just wait for my good news.

275
00:11:28,060 --> 00:11:28,990
You've got this.

276
00:11:34,220 --> 00:11:36,470
[2025 Shanghai College Entrance Exam]

277
00:11:36,490 --> 00:11:37,870
[Comprehensive Analysis Report]

278
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:40,050
[Current Exam Site Distribution]

279
00:11:45,840 --> 00:11:48,570
How long is the walk from
our hotel to the exam site?

280
00:11:48,570 --> 00:11:50,290
11 minutes from the lobby.

281
00:11:53,860 --> 00:11:54,910
You've visited the site in person?

282
00:11:54,910 --> 00:11:55,950
Yes,

283
00:11:56,140 --> 00:11:57,360
I checked it out myself.

284
00:11:57,360 --> 00:11:59,250
The new site is Xinhua Finance and
Economics Technical School.

285
00:11:59,250 --> 00:12:00,360
30 classrooms total,

286
00:12:00,360 --> 00:12:01,880
30 seats per classroom,

287
00:12:01,900 --> 00:12:03,600
900 exam-takers in total.

288
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:04,200
Exactly.

289
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:05,320
Once Ms. Xu told me the details,

290
00:12:05,320 --> 00:12:07,850
