600 RMB per night.

315
00:12:46,030 --> 00:12:48,320
That leaves us 500 RMB in
net profit per room.

316
00:12:48,320 --> 00:12:50,270
The margin isn't huge,
but it's far better

317
00:12:50,270 --> 00:12:51,360
