325
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:05,480
Not necessarily.

326
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:07,910
We're in the digital live-stream era now.

327
00:13:07,910 --> 00:13:10,600
Our hotel has an annual
partnership package

328
00:13:10,600 --> 00:13:11,840
with Dianjiangchun's live-stream team.

329
00:13:11,840 --> 00:13:12,720
I suggest

330
00:13:12,720 --> 00:13:13,960
