reasoning behind it.

356
00:13:56,740 --> 00:13:58,440
We’ve run multiple joint promotions

357
00:13:58,440 --> 00:14:00,150
with Dianjiangchun before,

358
00:14:00,150 --> 00:14:01,360
and the results were consistently strong.

359
00:14:01,360 --> 00:14:02,880
Platform big data shows

360
00:14:02,910 --> 00:14:04,600
the core audience interested
in our hotel promotions

361
00:14:04,600 --> 00:14:05,360
are

362
00:14:05,360 --> 00:14:06,480
middle-aged residents

363
00:14:06,480 --> 00:14:08,670
aged 40 to 50 in Shanghai.

364
00:14:08,790 --> 00:14:11,510
And this group overlaps heavily
with our target customers—

365
00:14:11,510 --> 00:14:14,440
families of exam-takers.

366
00:14:14,670 --> 00:14:16,550
By tagging our promotions with

367
00:14:16,550 --> 00:14:17,790
“Purong Hotel”

368
00:14:17,790 --> 00:14:19,670
and “college entrance exam”,

369
00:14:19,750 --> 00:14:20,440
I think

370
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:22,030
we'll drastically boost

371
00:14:22,030 --> 00:14:23,290
targeting precision.

372
00:14:24,320 --> 00:14:25,970
Indeed, you're right on

373
00:14:26,080 --> 00:14:28,200
