569
00:23:22,490 --> 00:23:23,220
Don't worry.

570
00:23:23,320 --> 00:23:24,390
Here, take your phone.

571
00:23:24,390 --> 00:23:25,540
Go on in.

572
00:23:26,810 --> 00:23:27,500
Coming.

573
00:23:36,970 --> 00:23:37,550
[Purong Hotel Exam Week Promotion Plan]

574
00:23:37,570 --> 00:23:38,520
[Campaign Background]

575
00:23:38,550 --> 00:23:40,630
[Customized Services][Exclusive Floors
for Exam Families]

576
00:23:39,200 --> 00:23:39,880
Mr. Wei said

577
00:23:39,880 --> 00:23:41,400
this plan works perfectly

578
00:23:40,660 --> 00:23:41,860
[Nutritious Set Meals]

579
00:23:41,420 --> 00:23:42,190
for Kuanli Hotel too.

580
00:23:42,190 --> 00:23:43,790
Please take a look, Mr. Duan.

581
00:23:47,110 --> 00:23:48,200
Ji Feng,

582
00:23:48,640 --> 00:23:50,310
you'll never guess.

583
00:23:50,310 --> 00:23:51,440
All your hard work

584
00:23:51,440 --> 00:23:53,480
ended up handing me a huge opportunity.

585
00:23:53,480 --> 00:23:55,650
Revise this plan quickly

586
00:23:55,680 --> 00:23:57,640
and send it to our senior
management group.

587
00:23:57,640 --> 00:23:58,920
Make sure my dad sees it.

588
00:23:58,920 --> 00:23:59,510
Got it.

589
00:23:59,530 --> 00:24:01,920
Are we still sticking with Dianjiangchun
for the live stream?

590
00:24:01,920 --> 00:24:03,550
Should we find a new host instead?

591
00:24:03,550 --> 00:24:04,830
Keep Dianjiangchun.

592
00:24:05,030 --> 00:24:06,110
She's the perfect ready-made option.

593
00:24:06,110 --> 00:24:07,840
But isn't she Ji Feng's person?

594
00:24:09,110 --> 00:24:11,650
You underestimate Ms. Jiang.

595
00:24:12,070 --> 00:24:13,550
She answers to no one.

596
00:24:19,210 --> 00:24:19,860
Sis,

597
00:24:20,020 --> 00:24:21,750
it's Young Mr. Duan on the line.

598
00:24:28,520 --> 00:24:29,510
Hello, Mr. Duan.

599
00:24:29,720 --> 00:24:32,070
I thought Dianjiangchun
and our Kuanli Group

600
00:24:32,070 --> 00:24:33,690
were long-term strategic partners.

601
00:24:33,690 --> 00:24:35,550
Last time you hosted the Song
Banquet Chinese Gala

602
00:24:35,550 --> 00:24:36,790
at our hotel,

603
00:24:36,900 --> 00:24:39,600
the view count went through the roof.

604
00:24:39,620 --> 00:24:42,200
Why leave us out this time?

605
00:24:43,200 --> 00:24:44,720
No need for such harsh words.

606
00:24:44,720 --> 00:24:46,480
Our team has always hoped

607
00:24:46,480 --> 00:24:48,310
to deepen cooperation with Kuanli.

608
00:24:48,310 --> 00:24:49,840
Since you said it yourself,

609
00:24:49,960 --> 00:24:51,450
I'll cut to the chase.

610
00:24:51,470 --> 00:24:52,310
Kuanli is launching

611
00:24:52,310 --> 00:24:55,270
an exam room promotion soon.

612
00:24:55,400 --> 00:24:56,880
I'm wondering if Ms. Jiang

613
00:24:56,880 --> 00:24:58,880
could lend us a hand.

614
00:25:00,920 --> 00:25:02,000
I know

615
00:25:02,000 --> 00:25:03,400
your contract with Purong

616
00:25:03,400 --> 00:25:05,030
still hasn't been finalized.

617
00:25:05,030 --> 00:25:06,720
Hear our offer first.

618
00:25:06,850 --> 00:25:08,710
If you're willing to work with us,

619
00:25:08,880 --> 00:25:09,810
Duan Aoxiang always plays fair.

620
00:25:09,810 --> 00:25:10,880
Let's have an

621
00:25:10,920 --> 00:25:12,680
honest competition.

622
00:25:13,400 --> 00:25:14,160
Sure.

623
00:25:14,510 --> 00:25:16,040
When would you like to meet?

624
00:25:16,270 --> 00:25:17,110
Right now.

625
00:25:17,770 --> 00:25:18,830
Send me your address.

626
00:25:18,830 --> 00:25:19,550
No need.

627
00:25:19,960 --> 00:25:20,820
My car's parked

628
00:25:20,880 --> 00:25:22,940
right outside your office building.

629
00:25:25,310 --> 00:25:25,840
Alright,

630
00:25:26,220 --> 00:25:27,180
I'm on my way.

631
00:25:37,260 --> 00:25:38,180
Zhenzhen,

632
00:25:39,640 --> 00:25:41,350
don't stress too much.

633
00:25:41,440 --> 00:25:42,690
[Shanghai Hongkou District
Central Hospital]

634
00:25:42,640 --> 00:25:45,680
The doctor said there's still hope.

635
00:25:42,710 --> 00:25:43,900
[Pathological Diagnosis Report]

636
00:25:46,550 --> 00:25:47,880
Our Yucheng

637
00:25:48,680 --> 00:25:50,590
still has a chance.

638
00:26:10,590 --> 00:26:11,670
Door unlocked.

639
00:26:11,700 --> 00:26:13,230
Hello, your food delivery.

640
00:26:15,880 --> 00:26:16,830
Takeout again,

641
00:26:16,830 --> 00:26:17,760
always takeout.

642
00:26:17,880 --> 00:26:19,440
Is it really that hard
to cook

643
00:26:19,440 --> 00:26:20,770
a proper meal for my son?

644
00:26:57,030 --> 00:26:57,830
Ms. Xu.

645
00:26:57,920 --> 00:27:00,480
word is Kuanli Hotel across the street
is also launching exam week promotions.

646
00:27:00,480 --> 00:27:01,200
Really?

647
00:27:01,730 --> 00:27:02,930
How did you hear that?

648
00:27:03,160 --> 00:27:05,550
A girl from the lobby bar said.

649
00:27:05,740 --> 00:27:06,550
She accidentally

650
00:27:06,550 --> 00:27:08,830
overheard Young Mr. Duan
on the phone yesterday

651
00:27:08,830 --> 00:27:11,090
and got chewed out badly.

652
00:27:11,180 --> 00:27:13,640
He mentioned Kuanli just

653
00:27:13,640 --> 00:27:15,680
signed a top streamer

654
00:27:15,680 --> 00:27:17,480
for their exam season campaign.

655
00:27:18,830 --> 00:27:19,640
Ms. Xu,

656
00:27:19,980 --> 00:27:21,960
isn't this suspicious?

657
00:27:21,990 --> 00:27:24,510
We just finalized our exam week plan,

658
00:27:24,510 --> 00:27:26,680
and Kuanli copies us right away.

659
00:27:27,440 --> 00:27:28,160
Eat first.

660
00:27:28,440 --> 00:27:29,700
I'll go check this out.

661
00:27:35,030 --> 00:27:35,440
Mr. Ji,

662
00:27:35,440 --> 00:27:36,160
the Sales Department

663
00:27:36,160 --> 00:27:37,790
pulled an all-nighter
to finish this live stream contract.

664
00:27:37,790 --> 00:27:39,070
Mr. Qian has already reviewed it.

665
00:27:39,070 --> 00:27:40,130
Please take a look.

666
00:27:40,720 --> 00:27:42,110
These are our online marketing plans

667
00:27:42,110 --> 00:27:43,550
to support the live event.

668
00:27:43,550 --> 00:27:44,830
Please review them as well.

669
00:27:44,830 --> 00:27:45,750
And these

670
00:27:45,750 --> 00:27:47,000
offline promotion materials drafted

671
00:27:47,000 --> 00:27:48,710
by the Communications Team
on Mr. Qian's request.

672
00:27:48,710 --> 00:27:49,880
Kindly check for revisions.

673
00:27:49,880 --> 00:27:51,610
and see if there are any issues.

674
00:27:52,110 --> 00:27:53,920
Is Mr. Qian in his office?

675
00:27:53,920 --> 00:27:55,030
Mr. Qian is...

676
00:27:56,880 --> 00:27:57,680
Mr. Ji,

677
00:27:57,880 --> 00:27:59,030
you were looking for me?

678
00:27:59,030 --> 00:28:00,450
Speak of the devil.

679
00:28:00,640 --> 00:28:01,350
Come in,

680
00:28:01,350 --> 00:28:02,010
take a seat.

681
00:28:09,200 --> 00:28:10,590
It seems the Sales Department

682
00:28:10,590 --> 00:28:13,250
takes this live stream project
very seriously.

683
00:28:13,310 --> 00:28:14,350
You put together

684
00:28:14,350 --> 00:28:16,830
such thorough reports in no time.

685
00:28:17,510 --> 00:28:18,790
Great work.

686
00:28:19,110 --> 00:28:20,160
Mr. Ji.

687
00:28:20,160 --> 00:28:21,350
To be honest,

688
00:28:21,530 --> 00:28:23,300
I know next to nothing

689
00:28:23,330 --> 00:28:24,640
about livestreaming.

690
00:28:24,640 --> 00:28:26,520
I'm totally old-school.

691
00:28:26,880 --> 00:28:27,880
Luckily,

692
00:28:27,880 --> 00:28:30,800
one of my team members stepped up.

693
00:28:31,350 --> 00:28:33,190
very document you see today

694
00:28:33,350 --> 00:28:35,640
was single-handedly done by her.

695
00:28:36,110 --> 00:28:37,070
Otherwise,

696
00:28:37,070 --> 00:28:38,960
I'd have nothing to present.

697
00:28:39,640 --> 00:28:41,590
Who's this unsung hero?

698
00:28:42,110 --> 00:28:43,350
Lu Zhenzhen.

699
00:28:46,880 --> 00:28:47,720
Mr. Ji,

700
00:28:48,350 --> 00:28:49,990
forgive me for saying so.

701
00:28:50,390 --> 00:28:51,990
Lu Zhenzhen.

702
00:28:52,110 --> 00:28:52,680
Yes?

703
00:28:52,920 --> 00:28:53,650
She's young,

704
00:28:53,880 --> 00:28:56,880
and sometimes reckless,

705
00:28:56,900 --> 00:28:58,470
but there's no denying

706
00:28:58,680 --> 00:28:59,480
she's capable

707
00:28:59,750 --> 00:29:00,830
and driven.

708
00:29:01,680 --> 00:29:02,830
Don't you agree?

709
00:29:05,030 --> 00:29:06,360
Have some tea, Mr. Qian.

710
00:29:09,210 --> 00:29:10,320
Of course,

711
00:29:10,720 --> 00:29:13,540
I don't want to overpraise my staff.

712
00:29:13,640 --> 00:29:16,260
But livestreaming

713
00:29:16,660 --> 00:29:18,340
is brand-new territory

714
00:29:18,370 --> 00:29:20,310
for Purong.

715
00:29:20,720 --> 00:29:23,000
If you're looking for someone

716
00:29:23,030 --> 00:29:25,640
experienced and reliable,

717
00:29:26,510 --> 00:29:29,070
Ms. Lu is the perfect candidate.

718
00:29:29,960 --> 00:29:31,890
Thank you for the recommendation.

719
00:29:32,350 --> 00:29:33,960
I've noticed Ms. Lu's

720
00:29:33,960 --> 00:29:35,360
outstanding performance.

721
00:29:35,360 --> 00:29:36,160
Rest assured.

722
00:29:36,160 --> 00:29:37,110
Great,

723
00:29:42,710 --> 00:29:44,030
this tea is excellent.

724
00:29:48,620 --> 00:29:50,510
Secretary Wu, I need to see
Mr. Ji urgently.

725
00:29:50,510 --> 00:29:51,200
Do you have an appointment?

726
00:29:51,200 --> 00:29:52,260
Good day, Mr. Qian.

727
00:29:54,200 --> 00:29:55,100
Mr. Qian.

728
00:29:59,270 --> 00:30:00,030
What's wrong?

729
00:30:00,030 --> 00:30:01,200
Kuanli

730
00:30:01,270 --> 00:30:03,200
is copying our exam week campaign?

731
00:30:03,750 --> 00:30:05,150
Where did this come from?

732
00:30:05,310 --> 00:30:06,400
One of the lobby bar staff

733
00:30:06,400 --> 00:30:08,400
overheard Mr. Duan's private call.

734
00:30:20,110 --> 00:30:20,790
Brother,

735
00:30:21,000 --> 00:30:22,060
It's pouring rain,

736
00:30:27,240 --> 00:30:28,640
and he's out running.

737
00:30:29,580 --> 00:30:31,110
Always worrying people sick.

738
00:30:31,110 --> 00:30:31,950
Jeez.

739
00:31:08,460 --> 00:31:09,560
Take a look.

740
00:31:08,590 --> 00:31:13,070
[Live Stream Cooperation Proposal
Exam Week Promotion]

741
00:31:17,430 --> 00:31:19,270
I haven't signed our contract yet,

742
00:31:19,270 --> 00:31:21,330
but I can't hold them off much longer.

743
00:31:21,680 --> 00:31:23,260
Duan Aoxiang is offering

744
00:31:23,280 --> 00:31:25,310
the streamer
a 40% revenue split —

745
00:31:25,640 --> 00:31:27,400
the highest rate in the industry.

746
00:31:27,400 --> 00:31:28,480
Our board now prefers

747
00:31:28,480 --> 00:31:30,630
letting your two hotels compete
head-to-head.

748
00:31:30,630 --> 00:31:32,690
This puts you at a huge disadvantage.

749
00:31:32,830 --> 00:31:33,960
As long as Purong

750
00:31:33,960 --> 00:31:35,480
gets to join the competition.

751
00:31:35,480 --> 00:31:37,540
But what if they cut you out entirely?

752
00:31:38,570 --> 00:31:41,420
My team is being pushed to
prioritize Kuanli first,

753
00:31:41,420 --> 00:31:42,850
streaming their promotion

754
00:31:42,850 --> 00:31:43,990
before yours.

755
00:31:44,110 --> 00:31:45,420
Can you accept that?

756
00:31:47,590 --> 00:31:48,440
I accept.

757
00:31:48,790 --> 00:31:50,020
You're really okay with this?

758
00:31:50,020 --> 00:31:52,560
All your early research
and promotion costs

759
00:31:52,590 --> 00:31:54,480
will only benefit Kuanli.

760
00:31:54,510 --> 00:31:56,510
They're reaping all your hard work.

761
00:31:59,350 --> 00:32:00,550
What if I run

762
00:32:00,670 --> 00:32:02,190
an extra live stream for you

763
00:32:02,190 --> 00:32:03,550
the day before their broadcast,

764
00:32:03,550 --> 00:32:04,550
using my personal backup account?

765
00:32:04,550 --> 00:32:05,200
No.

766
00:32:05,480 --> 00:32:06,640
That would break industry rules.

767
00:32:06,640 --> 00:32:08,550
But they stole our idea first.

768
00:32:16,270 --> 00:32:17,550
Let me ask you one thing.

769
00:32:17,550 --> 00:32:20,550
Was Duan Aoxiang your main contact?

770
00:32:28,640 --> 00:32:31,300
Mr. Ji, did you approve
letting Kuanli go first?

771
00:32:31,330 --> 00:32:32,120
I did.

772
00:32:33,340 --> 00:32:34,200
You knew perfectly well

773
00:32:34,200 --> 00:32:36,070
they copied our concept.

774
00:32:36,070 --> 00:32:37,820
If they launch ahead of us,

775
00:32:37,850 --> 00:32:39,570
all our effort will be for nothing.

776
00:32:39,570 --> 00:32:40,570
It won't be wasted.

777
00:32:40,570 --> 00:32:42,490
No single hotel can

778
00:32:42,510 --> 00:32:44,800
monopolize this business.

779
00:32:45,550 --> 00:32:47,070
Let them take the lead,

780
00:32:47,070 --> 00:32:48,000
build momentum,

781
00:32:48,000 --> 00:32:49,310
heat up the market.

782
00:32:49,340 --> 00:32:51,340
Then we step in and ride the wave.

783
00:32:51,360 --> 00:32:52,270
It works in our favor.

784
00:32:52,270 --> 00:32:53,340
Are you serious?

785
00:32:53,360 --> 00:32:54,640
How many high-end hotel bookings

786
00:32:54,640 --> 00:32:56,460
can we realistically get
for exam families?

787
00:32:56,460 --> 00:32:58,110
If they take the first slice,

788
00:32:58,110 --> 00:32:59,880
there'll be nothing left for us.

789
00:32:59,880 --> 00:33:01,440
But the truth is,

790
00:33:01,680 --> 00:33:04,280
Dianjiangchun's contract
restricts her from

791
00:33:04,450 --> 00:33:05,720
breaking terms with Kuanli.

792
00:33:05,720 --> 00:33:08,350
So you'd sacrifice Purong's interests

793
00:33:08,350 --> 00:33:11,480
just to keep one streamer from breaking a deal?

794
00:33:08,390 --> 00:33:10,980
[General Manager's Office]

795
00:33:12,470 --> 00:33:15,500
[General Manager's Office]

796
00:33:22,350 --> 00:33:23,270
Do you trust me?

797
00:33:27,440 --> 00:33:29,520
Ms. Lu landed another big project?

798
00:33:30,270 --> 00:33:31,790
Dinner treat soon, Zhenzhen?

799
00:33:31,790 --> 00:33:32,550
I'm swamped.

800
00:33:32,550 --> 00:33:33,640
No time for treats.

801
00:33:34,030 --> 00:33:36,440
Quietly making big money, huh.

802
00:33:37,550 --> 00:33:38,590
Fine fine,

803
00:33:38,590 --> 00:33:41,450
I'll treat everyone to dinner
and karaoke tonight.

804
00:33:41,550 --> 00:33:43,270
Hey, party tonight?

805
00:33:43,270 --> 00:33:44,400
Everyone's invited if you're free.

806
00:33:44,400 --> 00:33:46,270
-Count me in.
-Thanks, Zhenzhen.

807
00:33:51,070 --> 00:33:51,330
[Mom]

808
00:33:53,770 --> 00:33:55,960
[Mom]

809
00:33:55,990 --> 00:33:57,020
[Incoming call rejected]

810
00:34:37,110 --> 00:34:38,449
Door unlocked.

811
00:34:40,280 --> 00:34:41,810
Mom, why are you still here?

812
00:34:42,070 --> 00:34:43,030
I've been waiting for you

813
00:34:43,030 --> 00:34:45,030
to talk about Yucheng's surgery.

814
00:34:45,550 --> 00:34:47,610
Why are you working overtime so late?

815
00:34:52,320 --> 00:34:53,630
Where were you working?

816
00:34:53,630 --> 00:34:55,000
You smell like hot pot.

817
00:34:55,070 --> 00:34:56,130
I ordered takeout.

818
00:35:07,510 --> 00:35:08,670
This surgery slot

819
00:35:08,670 --> 00:35:11,440
was only secured through connections
by Yucheng's father.

820
00:35:11,440 --> 00:35:13,510
You have to take time off work.

821
00:35:14,650 --> 00:35:15,540
[Surgery Informed Consent Form]

822
00:35:15,540 --> 00:35:17,110
[Medical]

823
00:35:16,280 --> 00:35:17,510
The day after tomorrow?

824
00:35:17,510 --> 00:35:18,550
I have to work the day after tomorrow.

825
00:35:18,550 --> 00:35:19,800
Just ask for leave.

826
00:35:19,840 --> 00:35:21,840
Yucheng needs hospitalization and surgery,

827
00:35:21,840 --> 00:35:24,040
there's endless paperwork to sort out.

828
00:35:24,450 --> 00:35:26,700
Mom, I really can't.

829
00:35:27,280 --> 00:35:29,110
I have a critical live stream that day,

830
00:35:29,110 --> 00:35:30,280
and I have to supervise the whole thing.

831
00:35:30,280 --> 00:35:31,800
What's a live stream compared to this?

832
00:35:31,800 --> 00:35:33,590
Your husband's going into surgery!

833
00:35:33,590 --> 00:35:35,450
Can't you tell what matters more?

834
00:35:36,350 --> 00:35:38,480
If this surgery
can truly heal Yucheng

835
00:35:38,480 --> 00:35:39,480
and let him

836
00:35:39,480 --> 00:35:40,920
go back to work,

837
00:35:41,070 --> 00:35:43,760
I'll resign on the spot to
take care of him full-time.

838
00:35:43,760 --> 00:35:45,630
But if there's no real
guarantee of recovery,

839
00:35:45,630 --> 00:35:47,480
why do we all keep draining each other?

840
00:35:47,480 --> 00:35:49,280
Why not just mind our
own duties?

841
00:35:49,960 --> 00:35:51,280
"Own duties"?

842
00:35:51,300 --> 00:35:52,420
Let me ask you.

843
00:35:52,450 --> 00:35:53,890
Since my son fell ill,

844
00:35:53,920 --> 00:35:55,630
have you fulfilled your duties as a wife?

845
00:35:55,630 --> 00:35:57,480
Have you taken care of his daily life?

846
00:35:57,480 --> 00:35:59,880
What exactly have you done
for this family?

847
00:36:00,670 --> 00:36:02,760
I'm the one bringing
in the income.

848
00:36:02,840 --> 00:36:04,110
I'm out working every day, pregnant,

849
00:36:04,110 --> 00:36:05,440
coming home late every night.

850
00:36:05,440 --> 00:36:06,360
Do you think I want this life?

851
00:36:06,360 --> 00:36:07,710
With Nie Yucheng like this now,

852
00:36:07,710 --> 00:36:08,550
If I stop working

853
00:36:08,550 --> 00:36:09,550
and earning now,

854
00:36:09,550 --> 00:36:11,190
how will this family survive?

855
00:36:11,190 --> 00:36:12,630
Empty words.

856
00:36:13,230 --> 00:36:15,290
Do you really pay for this household?

857
00:36:15,440 --> 00:36:17,000
Everything my son earned

858
00:36:17,000 --> 00:36:18,400
fed you, clothed you,

859
00:36:18,400 --> 00:36:19,590
bought your school-district apartment,

860
00:36:19,590 --> 00:36:21,110
and paid for your premium

861
00:36:21,130 --> 00:36:22,320
maternity hospital.

862
00:36:22,320 --> 00:36:23,580
That's all in the past.

863
00:36:24,230 --> 00:36:26,840
The maternity center deposit
was fully refunded.

864
00:36:26,840 --> 00:36:29,170
All our savings went to his medical bills.

865
00:36:29,840 --> 00:36:31,550
Did you ever ask me?

866
00:36:31,550 --> 00:36:32,750
Did I ever agree all these?

867
00:36:32,750 --> 00:36:34,100
Did you ever discuss this with me?

868
00:36:34,100 --> 00:36:34,950
This...

869
00:36:35,080 --> 00:36:36,850
Discuss what?

870
00:36:37,070 --> 00:36:39,440
When family is sick, saving
them comes first.

871
00:36:39,440 --> 00:36:40,240
What about me?

872
00:36:42,030 --> 00:36:44,090
Do I have to sacrifice my whole future

873
00:36:44,510 --> 00:36:45,930
to live an exhausted half-life?

874
00:36:45,930 --> 00:36:47,920
An exhausted half-life?

875
00:36:48,030 --> 00:36:49,480
Watch your mouth.

876
00:36:49,480 --> 00:36:51,190
I'll slap some sense into you.

877
00:36:51,190 --> 00:36:52,440
Try me.

878
00:36:52,910 --> 00:36:53,790
Let me tell you,

879
00:36:54,230 --> 00:36:55,840
This is my home now.

880
00:36:55,860 --> 00:36:57,040
Get out.

881
00:36:57,630 --> 00:36:59,400
Leave right now.

882
00:36:59,960 --> 00:37:00,880
Get out!

883
00:37:12,810 --> 00:37:15,140
Blood… you're bleeding.

884
00:37:15,550 --> 00:37:16,760
My grandson!

885
00:37:16,880 --> 00:37:18,110
My grandson!

886
00:37:25,590 --> 00:37:27,220
[Hotel Detailed Management]

887
00:37:27,380 --> 00:37:29,720
[The characteristics of hotel
corporate culture]

888
00:37:39,270 --> 00:37:40,020
Mr. Ji,

889
00:37:42,030 --> 00:37:43,160
I need to talk to you.

890
00:37:43,990 --> 00:37:44,800
Sure.

891
00:37:54,150 --> 00:37:55,070
Help!

892
00:37:57,440 --> 00:37:58,590
Somebody!

893
00:37:59,670 --> 00:38:00,920
What's wrong?

894
00:38:01,650 --> 00:38:02,650
Where's my baby?

895
00:38:02,790 --> 00:38:04,590
Your baby's in the neonatal ICU.

896
00:38:05,360 --> 00:38:06,470
And my family?

897
00:38:06,890 --> 00:38:08,990
They're all with the baby.

898
00:38:11,550 --> 00:38:13,190
Your little one is premature,

899
00:38:13,190 --> 00:38:14,840
very fragile right now.

900
00:38:16,030 --> 00:38:17,690
I want to transfer hospitals.

901
00:38:18,330 --> 00:38:20,850
I can't help with that.

902
00:38:20,880 --> 00:38:21,840
Wait till the doctor's here.

903
00:38:21,840 --> 00:38:23,700
You'll need to talk to the doctor.

904
00:38:24,250 --> 00:38:25,340
Please leave.

905
00:38:25,920 --> 00:38:28,030
Your bed pad needs changing.

906
00:38:28,030 --> 00:38:30,960
-Untreated lochia will make you sick.
-I said leave!

907
00:38:31,710 --> 00:38:32,550
Now.

908
00:38:38,090 --> 00:38:39,160
Excuse me,

909
00:38:39,180 --> 00:38:40,660
could I borrow this stool?

910
00:38:43,180 --> 00:38:44,450
Thank you.

911
00:38:55,890 --> 00:38:58,870
[Lobby Lounge]

912
00:38:56,650 --> 00:38:58,230
Our Sales rep for

913
00:38:58,520 --> 00:38:59,480
tomorrow's live stream

914
00:38:59,480 --> 00:39:00,880
has a last-minute emergency.

915
00:39:00,880 --> 00:39:02,040
Who is it?

916
00:39:02,070 --> 00:39:02,910
Lu Zhenzhen.

917
00:39:03,690 --> 00:39:04,820
What happened?

918
00:39:05,480 --> 00:39:06,920
She's been admitted to hospital.

919
00:39:06,920 --> 00:39:08,570
We don't know the full details yet,

920
00:39:08,570 --> 00:39:10,410
but she definitely can't make it tomorrow.

921
00:39:10,410 --> 00:39:11,500
What do we do about the live stream then?

922
00:39:11,500 --> 00:39:12,570
That's why I came to find you.

923
00:39:12,570 --> 00:39:13,480
I think

924
00:39:13,920 --> 00:39:15,480
you're the perfect person to take over.

925
00:39:15,480 --> 00:39:16,320
Me?

926
00:39:16,760 --> 00:39:17,940
I know nothing about sales.

927
00:39:17,940 --> 00:39:18,940
You don't need to.

928
00:39:20,030 --> 00:39:22,190
Though the Purong Hotel
exam-week promotion

929
00:39:22,190 --> 00:39:23,670
falls under

930
00:39:23,670 --> 00:39:24,930
the Sales Department,

931
00:39:24,930 --> 00:39:25,560
but

932
00:39:25,590 --> 00:39:28,400
you're the one who created this project
from the start.

933
00:39:28,400 --> 00:39:29,590
You handled all the research,

934
00:39:29,590 --> 00:39:32,470
planning and internal proposals.

935
00:39:32,840 --> 00:39:33,760
You know

936
00:39:33,760 --> 00:39:35,490
every detail of this campaign,

937
00:39:35,760 --> 00:39:36,820
and you understand

938
00:39:36,920 --> 00:39:38,450
exactly what parents need.

939
00:39:39,030 --> 00:39:42,110
You're also the one who convinced me

940
00:39:42,880 --> 00:39:44,480
to launch this online promotion.

941
00:39:44,480 --> 00:39:45,230
I believe

942
00:39:45,380 --> 00:39:46,770
You're far better than Ms. Lu

943
00:39:46,770 --> 00:39:48,480
at presenting its true value.

944
00:39:52,230 --> 00:39:53,070
Alright,

945
00:39:53,710 --> 00:39:54,590
I'll try.

946
00:39:56,840 --> 00:39:59,110
But I need two favors.

947
00:39:59,920 --> 00:40:01,440
First,

948
00:40:01,440 --> 00:40:02,400
please arrange

949
00:40:02,400 --> 00:40:04,030
a temporary lobby manager

950
00:40:04,030 --> 00:40:05,290
to cover my shift here.

951
00:40:05,480 --> 00:40:07,190
Second…

952
00:40:07,190 --> 00:40:09,650
Take over the Jazz Bar
performance tonight.

953
00:40:11,730 --> 00:40:13,260
I'll get everything ready.

954
00:40:18,630 --> 00:40:19,890
After the live stream…

955
00:40:20,360 --> 00:40:21,480
I have something to say to you.

